Comment: 0,0:16:41.80,0:16:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,空太是笨蛋的「SA」
Comment: 0,0:16:43.34,0:16:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這句哪裡都沒有「SA」啊!
Comment: 0,0:16:47.21,0:16:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,諸君 我們終於迎接這個時刻了!
Comment: 0,0:16:50.50,0:16:51.64,Upside,,0,0,0,karaoke,快下來 學姐
Comment: 0,0:16:49.02,0:16:50.50,Upside,,0,0,0,karaoke,看到 內褲了啊!
Comment: 0,0:16:51.45,0:16:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,櫻花莊最強戰士們聚集的這個時候
Comment: 0,0:16:54.17,0:16:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,集結我們友情的力量 來支配文化祭吧！
Comment: 0,0:16:57.65,0:16:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,也就是說
Comment: 0,0:16:59.13,0:17:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,在文化祭的時候 以櫻花莊為名來製作個什麼
Comment: 0,0:17:04.80,0:17:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我是沒有問題
Comment: 0,0:17:06.27,0:17:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,好像很有趣
Comment: 0,0:17:08.00,0:17:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我也是贊成...
Comment: 0,0:17:10.36,0:17:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,龍之介也沒問題
Comment: 0,0:17:12.36,0:17:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,全員贊成 決定了!
Comment: 0,0:17:14.91,0:17:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,都要做了 就做些櫻花莊特色的東西吧
Comment: 0,0:17:18.20,0:17:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,話是這麼說
Comment: 0,0:17:19.48,0:17:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,美咲和椎名作畫
Comment: 0,0:17:22.02,0:17:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,仁是劇本
Comment: 0,0:17:23.34,0:17:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,青山是聲優
Comment: 0,0:17:25.01,0:17:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,有這些要素的話 似乎可以做出很厲害的東西
Comment: 0,0:17:29.05,0:17:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不僅如此 櫻花莊還有飛龍在喔 程式設計師
Comment: 0,0:17:33.10,0:17:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,飛龍?
Comment: 0,0:17:33.98,0:17:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,是指赤板
Comment: 0,0:17:35.23,0:17:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,龍之介 所以是飛龍
Comment: 0,0:17:37.24,0:17:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那像是遊戲那樣 用搖桿操作怎麼樣?
Comment: 0,0:17:40.98,0:17:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,原來如此
Comment: 0,0:17:41.82,0:17:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,但是那樣的話 一次只能一個人玩
Comment: 0,0:17:45.70,0:17:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,看能不能做成所有觀眾都可以遊玩的
Comment: 0,0:17:49.70,0:17:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,所有人?
Comment: 0,0:17:51.00,0:17:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,例如觀眾一起拍手的話 角色就會跳或舉手
Comment: 0,0:17:55.84,0:18:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,就是說 大家一起合力推進故事 能不能製做成這樣?
Comment: 0,0:18:01.06,0:18:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,恩?
Comment: 0,0:18:05.37,0:18:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,就是這個啊 後輩!
Comment: 0,0:18:07.30,0:18:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這個我也覺得很有趣
Comment: 0,0:18:08.62,0:18:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我也覺得很不錯
Comment: 0,0:18:10.04,0:18:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,很好!不愧是後輩!
Comment: 0,0:18:12.34,0:18:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,馬上就向龍之介報告
Comment: 0,0:18:14.17,0:18:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,決定好了的話 就要盡快向學生會提出申請喔
Comment: 0,0:18:17.89,0:18:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,沒有許可的話 是不可以參加的
Comment: 0,0:18:20.94,0:18:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,學生會嗎?
Comment: 0,0:18:22.65,0:18:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,怎麼了嗎?
Comment: 0,0:18:23.70,0:18:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,啊 沒什麼
Comment: 0,0:18:25.01,0:18:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,如果是這樣的話 就要快點決定內容了啊
Comment: 0,0:18:28.11,0:18:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,從頭開始製作的話 時間可是很緊迫的啊
Comment: 0,0:18:32.56,0:18:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,喵波隆
Comment: 0,0:18:34.88,0:18:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,就是那個啊 真白!
Comment: 0,0:18:36.17,0:18:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,龍之介說 如果從器材商那邊借器材的話
Comment: 0,0:18:39.18,0:18:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,空太的想法就有可能可以實現了
Comment: 0,0:18:41.47,0:18:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,真厲害 赤板到底是怎麼樣的人物啊
Comment: 0,0:18:44.41,0:18:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,非常好! 導演的職責就交給你了 後輩!
Comment: 0,0:18:47.96,0:18:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,咦?
Comment: 0,0:18:48.83,0:18:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,沒異議
Comment: 0,0:18:49.68,0:18:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,多指教囉 神田
Comment: 0,0:18:52.43,0:18:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,空太 加油
Comment: 0,0:18:55.38,0:18:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,由我來監督協調這些人嗎...
Comment: 0,0:19:08.62,0:19:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,文化祭嗎? 看起來很有趣啊
Comment: 0,0:19:12.60,0:19:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不過似乎變成很困難的事情了
Comment: 0,0:19:15.00,0:19:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,麗塔
Comment: 0,0:19:15.96,0:19:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,怎麼了嗎?真白?
Comment: 0,0:19:17.43,0:19:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,麗塔 今天起 來我的房間睡
Comment: 0,0:19:20.35,0:19:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那是怎麼樣心境的變化呢?
Comment: 0,0:19:23.01,0:19:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,已經不能待在空太的房間了
Comment: 0,0:19:24.85,0:19:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我們男女關係可是很純潔的
Comment: 0,0:19:26.93,0:19:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,和仁不同 空太可是草食性男喔
Comment: 0,0:19:29.68,0:19:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我說!妳知道我的理性每天晚上都要經過多殘酷的戰鬥嗎?
Comment: 0,0:19:34.35,0:19:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我沒關係喔 去真白的房間睡
Comment: 0,0:19:37.22,0:19:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,但是我有一個條件 空太
Comment: 0,0:19:40.75,0:19:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我?
Comment: 0,0:19:41.46,0:19:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這個周末 和我約會吧
Comment: 0,0:19:48.01,0:19:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這...這裡是...
Comment: 0,0:19:50.81,0:19:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,約會的目的地
Comment: 0,0:19:52.50,0:19:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這裡是酒店啊!
Comment: 0,0:19:54.21,0:19:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,沒錯
Comment: 0,0:19:55.20,0:19:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你可別在酒店面前抵抗 讓女孩子感到難堪喔
Comment: 0,0:19:58.91,0:20:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不不不  還是等一下吧!
Comment: 0,0:20:02.06,0:20:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,別這樣!
Comment: 0,0:20:02.54,0:20:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我會很溫柔的~
Comment: 0,0:20:04.42,0:20:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,妳要對我做什麼啊!
Comment: 0,0:20:07.94,0:20:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,神田...
Comment: 0,0:20:14.74,0:20:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,真巧啊...
Comment: 0,0:20:17.66,0:20:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,是呀
Comment: 0,0:20:18.90,0:20:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,誰會相信這樣的巧合啊
Comment: 0,0:20:21.10,0:20:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,嘛...機會難得 四個人一起吧
Comment: 0,0:20:26.38,0:20:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,四個人?
Comment: 0,0:20:28.58,0:20:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,原來目的地是這裡啊
Comment: 0,0:20:32.93,0:20:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,總覺得有點緊張
Comment: 0,0:20:38.65,0:20:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,空太 這邊喔
Comment: 0,0:20:51.33,0:20:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,椎名?
Comment: 0,0:20:54.29,0:20:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我想讓你看的 是這張畫
Comment: 0,0:21:14.53,0:21:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這是真白來日本前 畫的最後一幅畫
Comment: 0,0:21:25.79,0:21:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,稍微了解一點了嗎?
Comment: 0,0:21:28.77,0:21:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,真白的事情
Comment: 0,0:21:39.54,0:21:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我看了真白在這邊所畫的漫畫
Comment: 0,0:21:44.03,0:21:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,雖然我不太瞭解漫畫
Comment: 0,0:21:47.08,0:21:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,但我不認為 真白要為此放棄作畫
Comment: 0,0:21:56.33,0:21:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你是怎麼想的呢?空太?
Comment: 0,0:22:06.01,0:22:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,椎名她...
Comment: 0,0:22:12.92,0:22:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,應該要回到藝術的世界
Comment: 0,0:22:16.85,0:23:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,ed,
Comment: 0,0:23:40.62,0:23:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我的生活表被一個女性食客給打亂了
Comment: 0,0:23:44.72,0:23:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke, 為什麼那個女人要在早上6點45分上廁所呢?
Comment: 0,0:23:47.92,0:23:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那是我的時間啊!!
